    "biography": "<p>The vengeful spirit of a woman burned in the witch trials (no accepted taxonomy). All Brocken bows have Essence Drain; roll 1D6 per other listed power — on a 1 that individual lacks it.</p><p><strong>Powers:</strong> Alienation (Zone ×2), Cold Aura (Personal), Darkness, Essence Drain (Permanent and Temporary), Fear (Zone ×2), Immunity to Age, Immunity to Cold, Immunity to Normal Weapons, Immunity to Pathogens, Immunity to Poisons, Manifestation, Movement, Paralyzing Touch</p><p><strong>Weaknesses:</strong> Allergy (Sunlight, Severe), Essence Loss (1 point per 10 years), Vulnerability (Fire)</p><p><em>Attacks: Special (Essence Drain, Paralyzing Touch). Habitat: Hills and mountains, wild lands. Range: Southeastern France, Germany (Franconia, Rhineland, Saxony). Dual-natured; Essence listed 7(A). Book Charisma 2/6. Cold Aura can be extended to one victim within Essence×D6 metres as a Complex Action. PAE p.21.</em></p>",
